videos.description: Kevon Looney dishes one out to Steph Curry who drains the 3 from the corner.

videos.headline: Steph knocks down the early 3

videos.description: Nuggets get out in transition as Jamal Murray throws the lob to Michael Porter Jr. for the two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Murray goes up top to Porter for the jam) 2021/04/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray goes up top to Porter for the jam

videos.description: Steph Curry flips in the layup for his 19th point as he passes Wilt Chamberlain to become the Warriors' all-time leading scorer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Steph's layup makes him Warriors' all-time leading scorer) 2021/04/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Steph's layup makes him Warriors' all-time leading scorer

videos.description: Kent Bazemore doesn't hit anything on his first free throw.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bazemore is WAY off on the free throw attempt) 2021/04/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bazemore is WAY off on the free throw attempt

videos.description: Jamal Murray goes between Kent Bazemore's legs to rip the ball away and finds Michael Porter Jr. for the easy dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Murray rips ball from underneath Bazemore’s legs for steal and Porter dunk) 2021/04/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray rips ball from underneath Bazemore's legs for steal and Porter dunk

videos.description: Steph Curry splashes a 3 on Facundo Campazzo and then says something to him as he heads back on defense.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Steph has words for Campazzo after splashing 3) 2021/04/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Steph has words for Campazzo after splashing 3

videos.description: Juan Toscano-Anderson and Monte Morris each get technical fouls after tensions flare following Toscano-Anderson's dunk.

videos.headline: Toscano-Anderson and Morris get into it after Toscano-Anderson's dunk

videos.description: JaVale McGee blocks Jordan Poole's dunk attempt, but the ball sticks on the rim and drops in.

videos.headline: Poole's dunk attempt gets blocked, but still goes in

videos.description: Jamal Murray is helped off the court with an apparent knee injury after driving to the basket.

videos.headline: Murray grabs his knee after driving to the basket

videos.description: Steph Curry goes off for 53 points as he passes Wilt Chamberlain as the top scorer in Warriors' history.
